{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 3:3Figure 3: Illustration of the comprehensive framework which encompasses: (a) CodeS that is incrementally pre-trained on top of StarCoder using our specially curated SQL-focused dataset.",
    "(b) Our unique method for database prompt construction.",
    "(c) The proposed bi-directional data augmentation technique for adapting to new domains.",
    "CodeS can be employed in two distinct manners: (d) Inferring after a supervised fine-tuning of CodeS on a training dataset, sourced from text-to-SQL benchmarks along with our enriched (question, SQL) pairs.",
    "(e) Direct inference through few-shot in-context learning on CodeS."
  ]
}